SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN T1.Segment = 'SME' THEN 'SME'
        WHEN T1.Segment = 'LAM' THEN 'LAM'
        WHEN T1.Segment = 'KAM' THEN 'KAM'
    END AS Segment,
    CASE 
        WHEN T3.MaxIncrease = 1 THEN 'Highest'
        WHEN T3.MinIncrease = 1 THEN 'Lowest'
        ELSE 'Neither'
    END AS Increase
FROM customers AS T1
INNER JOIN yearmonth AS T2
ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT 
        CASE 
            WHEN T1.Segment = 'SME' THEN 1
            WHEN T1.Segment = 'LAM' THEN 2
            WHEN T1.Segment = 'KAM' THEN 3
        END AS Segment,
        MAX(((SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END)) / SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END)) * 100) AS MaxIncrease,
        MIN(((SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END)) / SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END)) * 100) AS MinIncrease
    FROM customers AS T1
    INNER JOIN yearmonth AS T2
    ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE T1.Currency = 'EUR'
    GROUP BY T1.Segment
) AS T3
ON T1.Segment = CASE 
    WHEN T3.MaxIncrease = 1 THEN 'SME'
    WHEN T3.MaxIncrease = 2 THEN 'LAM'
    WHEN T3.MaxIncrease = 3 THEN 'KAM'
    WHEN T3.MinIncrease = 1 THEN 'SME'
    WHEN T3.MinIncrease = 2 THEN 'LAM'
    WHEN T3.MinIncrease = 3 THEN 'KAM'
END
WHERE T1.Currency = 'EUR'	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
